title: Friday Night Rivals Week 9: Highlights, scores, photos, and more
text:
Friday Night Rivals Week 9: Highlights, scores, photos, and more - WCIV-TV | ABC News 4 - Charleston News, Sports, Weather Member Center: Friday Night Rivals Week 9: Highlights, scores, photos, and more Posted: Updated: 
MOUNT PLEASANT, S.C. (WCIV) -- It's Week 9 of high school football in South Carolina and teams are starting that big march to playoffs and hopefully a state title bid. 
There are plenty of big games happening this week and ABC News 4 will have coverage of each one. The TruMoo Friday Night Rivals Game of the Week pits James Island against Cane Bay, two teams with records the don't tell the true story of their power. 
Complete post-game coverage starts at 11:05 p.m. on ABC News 4. 
Here's a list of the games we're tracking in Week 9: Stratford 7-34 West Ashley Cane Bay at James IslandWando 28-40 Goose Creek
